CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: American Integrity Insurance Group is a profitable and growing insurance group headquartered in Tampa, Florida. Through our insurance carrier subsidiary, American Integrity Insurance Company of Florida, we provide personal residential property insurance for single-family homeowners and condominium owners as well as coverage for vacant dwellings and investment properties, predominantly in Florida. We are the seventh largest writer of residential property insurance in Florida.
